ew\"/>\n| N/A\n| \u2013\n|-\n| 2006\n| Homan ([[City View Curling Club|CVCC]])\n| Skip\n| U18 International\n| 1st<ref name=\"Optimist\"/>\n| N/A\n| \u2013\n|-\n| 2007\n| Homan ([[City View Curling Club|CVCC]])\n| Skip\n| [[Pepsi Ontario Junior Curling Championships|Ontario Juniors]]\n| 3rd<ref name=\"2007juniors\"/>\n| N/A\n| \u2013\n|-\n| 2007\n| Ontario (Homan)\n| Skip\n| [[Curling at the 2007 Canada Games|Canada Winter Games]]\n| 1st\n| 7\u20130<ref name=\"ottawa2007\"/>\n| \u2013\n|-\n| 2008\n| Homan ([[Ottawa Curling Club|OCC]])\n| Skip\n| Ontario Juniors\n| 2nd\n| 6\u20134<ref>{{cite web |title=Homan |url=https://www.curlingzone.com/event.php?view=Team&eventid=1803&teamid=33558&profileid= |website=CurlingZone |accessdate=April 2, 2020}}</ref>\n| \u2013\n|-\n| 2009\n| Homan ([[Ottawa Curling Club|OCC]])\n| Skip\n| Ontario Juniors\n| 1st\n| 8\u20130<ref>{{cite news |last1=Fontaine |first1=Deyra |title=Ottawa curlers headed for nationals |url=https://capitalcurrent.ca/archive/centretownnews/1997-2016/2009/01/22/ottawa-curlers-headed-for-nationals/ |accessdate=April 7, 2020 |publisher=Centretown News |date=January 22, 2009}}</ref>\n| \u2013\n|-\n| 2009\n| Ontario (Homan)\n| Skip\n| [[2009 Canadian Junior Curling Championships|Canadian Juniors]]\n| 2nd\n| 10\u20133\n| 80<ref name=\"2009juniors\">{{cite web |title=2009 M&M Meat Shops Canadian Junior Curling Championship (W) |url=https://www.curling.ca/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/Junior_Women_2009.pdf |publisher=Canadian Curling Association |pages=2, 6|accessdate=April 2, 2020 |date=May 3, 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2009\n| Homan ([[Ottawa Curling Club|OCC]])\n| Skip\n| [[2009 Canadian Olympic Curling Trials#Pre-trials qualifier|Olympic Pre-Q]]\n| 5th\n| 3\u20133<ref name=\"2009rttr\"/>\n| 75<ref>{{cite news |title=Women's Cumulative Stats |url=https://issuu.com/curling/docs/2009rttr_morningroar_nov14 |accessdate=April 8, 2020 |work=The Morning Roar |publisher=Canadian Curling Association |date=November 14, 2009 |page=8}}</