-coach-1.4818893|title=Rachel Homan's new coach will get 'in your face'|date=September 11, 2008|work=CBC|access-date=March 30, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row| 2019\u201320 \n| Rachel Homan || Emma Miskew || Joanne Courtney || Lisa Weagle || Alternate Cheryl Kreviazuk for [[2020 Scotties Tournament of Hearts|Scotties]]<ref name=\"2020stoh\">{{cite web |title=2020 Scotties Tournament of Hearts: Ontario |url=https://www.curling.ca/scoreboard/#!/competitions/6241/teams/26884 |website=Curling Canada |accessdate=April 4, 2020}}</ref> || $35,300 (13th)<ref>{{cite web |title=World Curling Tour: Women's Ranking |url=https://www.worldcurl.com/ranking.php?et=21&eventyear=2020 |website=World Curling Tour |accessdate=April 3, 2020 |date=February 4, 2020}}</ref> || Marcel Rocque<ref name=\"2020stoh\"/>\n|}\n\n==Grand Slam record==\n{{Curling GS key}}\n{{clear}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Event\n! [[2008-09 curling season|2008\u201309]]\n! [[2009-10 curling season|2009\u201310]]\n! [[2010-11 curling season|2010\u201311]]\n! [[2011-12 curling season|2011\u201312]]\n! [[2012-13 curling season|2012\u201313]]\n! [[2013-14 curling season|2013\u201314]]\n! [[2014-15 curling season|2014\u201315]]\n! [[2015\u201316 curling season|2015\u201316]]\n! [[2016\u201317 curling season|2016\u201317]]\n! [[2017\u201318 curling season|2017\u201318]]\n! [[2018\u201319 curling season|2018\u201319]]\n! [[2019\u201320 curling season|2019\u201320]]\n|-\n| [[Masters of Curling|Masters]]\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | N/A\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | N/A\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | N/A\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | N/A\n|style=\"background:#0f0;\"| [[2012 The Masters Grand Slam of Curling|'''C''']]\n|style=\"background:#0f0;\"| [[2013 The Masters Grand Slam of Curling|'''C''']]\n|style=\"background:yellow;\"| [[2014 The Masters Grand Slam of Curling|SF]]\n|style=\"background:#0f0;\"| [[2015 The Masters Grand Slam of Curling|'''C''']]\n|style=\"background:thistle;\"| [