man.com/ Team Website]\n*{{worldcurl|10078}}\n*{{worldcurling|5927}}\n\n{{Footer World Curling Champions (women)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Homan, Rachel}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Ottawa]]\n[[Category:Curlers from Ontario]]\n[[Category:Canadian women curlers]]\n[[Category:Canadian women's curling champions]]\n[[Category:World curling champions]]\n[[Category:University of Ottawa alumni]]\n[[Category:Continental Cup of Curling participants]]\n[[Category:Curlers at the 2018 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic curlers of Canada]]\n[[Category:People from the County of St. Paul No. 19]]\n[[Category:Canada Cup (curling) participants]]\n", "name_user": "Allthegoldmedals", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMixed doubles:overlink", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rachel_Homan"}
